title: What Ridiculous Things About Sex Did You Believe Were True?
description:
Looking back at it, you can't believe you thought these things about sex when you were younger. If you've had a moment like this, we want to hear from you. 
But first, Bert has a " bless you heart" confession about something he learned last year.
